The '''Remote Terminator''' was an extremely strong [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage, the consumption of which was viewed by many in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] as an extremely risky proposition. Before mixing a Remote Terminator, it was common for a bartender to ask whether the patron wanted the ingredients mixed using a preprogrammed recipe, or for the ingredients to be mixed together randomly. The latter option was considered to be riskier than the former.

